2017-09-10T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"寫大陸字就係大陸學生?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031ed26a51df7c92c0d539077cb04c8bf64ed762","tid":394377,"uid":59142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"快d貼六四坦克碌豬論,貼埋馬力個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8f40b2edd3904b8699ed77059efdd4e98f93aa","tid":394377,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa9ab355635e706b7bf2b5dc1c94c3723b61c94","tid":394377,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"追殺香港年青人可以輕鬆刷政績<br />\n反正呢屆政府一上任就瘋狂追殺年青人<br />\n但講劉曉波就得罪中共 無利益得著 不了<br />\n<br />\n呢班高官權貴偽善醜陋到極<br />\n加上近年累積極大怨氣無法疏導<br />\n正正係網上瘋狂慶祝原因"},{"pid":"5ccbb43f4aabdae881a32191351b553323219d1f","tid":394377,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/m4s0vktj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm4s0vktj&h=f71f1c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸哩衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單嘢都唔關佢地事</blockquote><br />\n佢地知自己係雙重標準兩把尺，所以想轉移討論焦點，將事件講成香港學生插贓嫁禍&amp;nbsp;<br />\n都幾高明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估班中國人弱智？佢地梗係知道係玩野啦<br />\n不過佢地最鐘意就係轉移焦點<br />\n例如撕海報事件，明明焦點應該係有無權撕毀海報阻止人地既意見，就比班中國人轉移焦點去到香港學生既語文能力、應否港獨之類<br />\n今次都係，明明焦點係雙重標準，佢地就轉移焦點去嫁禍上面<br />\n<br />\n轉移視線係中國五毛最鐘意既招數，普通中國人見得多自然都非常熟識"},{"pid":"64ef0323a2a34cc5c550a488b073c98b3e4f10f3","tid":394377,"uid":12741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/m4s0vktj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm4s0vktj&h=f71f1c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸哩衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單嘢都唔關佢地事</blockquote><br />\n佢地知自己係雙重標準兩把尺，所以想轉移討論焦點，將事件講成香港學生插贓嫁禍&amp;nbsp;<br />\n都幾高明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估班中國人弱智？佢地梗係知道係玩野啦<br />\n不過佢地最鐘意就係轉移焦點<br />\n例如撕海報事件，明明焦點應該係有無權撕毀海報阻止人地既意見，就比班中國人轉移焦點去到香港學生既語文能力、應否港獨之類<br />\n今次都係，明明焦點係雙重標準，佢地就轉移焦點去嫁禍上面<br />\n<br />\n轉移視線係中國五毛最鐘意既招數，普通中國人見得多自然都非常熟識</blockquote><br />\n牛頭唔搭馬嘴先係高招<br />\n<br />\n到時大陸只會見到表面意思<br />\n<br />\n令到成單野各有各講 唔會對到質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e526c61122c35bca450f16b0cb09658fa7072f2","tid":394377,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd6bc3ee8611973cb7025a91200cf95c932e4a9","tid":394377,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:36:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b06c1d9355dd8ccb376148d311897c05d11c29f2","tid":394377,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"其實每次都可以咁玩，睇下政府/傳媒可以點雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de2a6220c1920cd8a69c97ac57982c998b936c5","tid":394377,"uid":141399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"支那人雙重標準係常識"},{"pid":"1eb9536c677d4f9175be2368401895a2caf834b0","tid":394377,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}